                            <comment id="12622854" author="dlx" created="Fri, 15 Aug 2008 11:03:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I updated the patch according to the latest changes in trunk. This is a diff against trunk 686186. I also added another test to demonstrate that &quot;124,,789&quot; or &quot;123,45&quot; parse without failure (with and without the fix).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12622858" author="shalinmangar" created="Fri, 15 Aug 2008 11:54:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changing issue type to bug because the current behavior can silently ignore part of the string leading to invalid/incomplete data with no notification to the user.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
